  "description": "The **major arcana** are the 22 trump cards in a tarot deck, numbered 0 (The Fool) through 21 (The World). They represent archetypal themes, life passages, and psychological forces that operate at a larger scale than the everyday situations depicted in the [minor arcana](./minor-arcana.md).",
